ok i sound like a noob but whats really the difference between this and Game.of.Thrones.S03E01.1080p.HDTV.x264-GOT [PublicHD]

A WEB-DL version is a version without the TV channels watermark on the image. The episode was pulled from a web feed of some sort, instead of through a chable/sattelite TV channel.
@Man_no9 Thank you. I've always wondered what WEB-DL really means ;)
